WEBVTT

00:01.200 --> 00:03.300
My name is 
Melinda Gordon.

00:03.400 --> 00:04.700
I'm married,

00:04.800 --> 00:06.900
I live in a small town,

00:07.000 --> 00:08.900
and I own an antique shop.

00:09.000 --> 00:11.000
I might be just like you,

00:11.100 --> 00:12.800
except that from the time
I was a little girl,

00:12.900 --> 00:15.100
I knew that I could
talk to the dead.

00:15.200 --> 00:16.500
It's all right, honey.

00:16.600 --> 00:19.800
Earthbound spirits,
my grandmother called them.

00:19.907 --> 00:22.400
They're stuck here because they have
unfinished business with the living

00:22.503 --> 00:26.207
and they come to me for help.

00:27.706 --> 00:33.105
In order to tell you my story,
I have to tell you theirs.

00:35.000 --> 00:41.074
